query:
SELECT id, userEmail, userName, enneagramType, LEFT(enneagramAnalysis, 200) as analysis_preview, createdAt
FROM conversations
WHERE id LIKE '%jhob86m66%'
ORDER BY createdAt DESC
LIMIT 1;
